ol.li:
If you want to reduce the client-side "Rendering" time:

Make as many elements as possible collapsed by default by
                  specifying the -oxy-foldable and -oxy-folded CSS
                  rules:section {
  -oxy-foldable: true;
}
* {
  -oxy-folded: true;
}

Hide irrelevant elements with the display:
                    none CSS rule.
